  <does rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</does>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">How do your Sites use and share my information? We use the information we collect about you to Fulfill your requests for products services and information including to send you electronic newsletters or complete a transaction that you have requested Enable you to participate in features such as surveys polls sweepstakes and message boards Provide you with electronic newsletters updates information special offers and promotional materials on behalf of our Sites and third parties in accordance with applicable law Analyze the use of our Sites and information about visitors to our Sites to understand and improve those Sites and our content offerings and in accordance with our sharing policies as stated below to produce anonymous or aggregated data and statistics that we may share with third parties Develop and produce advertising tailored to your interests as further described herein and Prevent potential illegal conduct or to address actual or suspected violations of our terms of use</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

